<p><em>Welcome to Chartography: insights and delights from the world of data storytelling. </em></p><p>A few sundries plucked from social media. Then: I got an early copy of <em>The Globemakers</em>, Peter Bellerby’s new book about his spherical beauties. Let’s take a look!</p><h2>Sundries</h2><p>🥵 Simple-charts decorate a series of environmental cards that remind me of 1970s paperback covers. (If only they were distressed.)</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fff34c04a-0355-4bcd-9d1f-11eb33260bf1_3106x2000.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/EzkayUbH9_jd9qN3USkPvLWTcHe7Kqw8L-LKXnKivAg=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmZjM0YzA0YS0wMzU1LTRiY2QtOWQxZi0xMWViMzMyNjBiZjFfMzEwNngyMDAwLnBuZw== 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/IwbAKY_ 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/4v2A_PGqXM_ 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux. 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/9grCRU4PPIvmZCZhdeNNjnweBtrBW06-djNTRk0APcg=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmZjM0YzA0YS0wMzU1LTRiY2QtOWQxZi0xMWViMzMyNjBiZjFfMzEwNngyMDAwLnBuZw== 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/GWgvoetzqAnA3ipYMqL3ezLog- 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p>There is a “Little Pictures” competition to make more. See details at the <a href="https://climate.esa.int/en/li